    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Win下安装python3和pip"><a href="#Win下安装python3和pip" class="headerlink" title="Win下安装python3和pip"></a>Win下安装python3和pip</h1><h2 id="Python3安装"><a href="#Python3安装" class="headerlink" title="Python3安装"></a>Python3安装</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://www.python.org/</span><br><span class="line">下载Python3安装包</span><br><span class="line">Win: https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.3/python-3.7.3-amd64.exe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/04/13/5cb1995531050.png" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/04/13/5cb199552664b.png" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/04/13/5cb19955323b4.png" alt="img"></p><h2 id="Pip安装"><a href="#Pip安装" class="headerlink" title="Pip安装"></a>Pip安装</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip 是 Python 的软件包安装程序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">访问 http://zuoshouzz.github.io/images/get-pip.py 下载脚本 get-ip.py</span><br><span class="line">访问 C:\Windows\system32 文件夹 ，打开 cmd 或者 cmd.exe</span><br><span class="line">cmd中输入 python get-pip.py路径即可</span><br><span class="line">cmd中输入 pip -V 查看pip版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/04/13/5cb1a2293ea58.png" alt="a5.png"></p><h2 id="相关python库安装"><a href="#相关python库安装" class="headerlink" title="相关python库安装"></a>相关python库安装</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">需要安装一下模块</span><br><span class="line">pillow</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Mac下安装python3和pip"><a href="#Mac下安装python3和pip" class="headerlink" title="Mac下安装python3和pip"></a>Mac下安装python3和pip</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://www.python.org/</span><br><span class="line">下载Python3安装包</span><br><span class="line">Mac: https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.7.3/python-3.7.3-macosx10.9.pkg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/04/13/5cb19c1499bbf.gif" alt="Untitled.gif"></p><h2 id="PIP安装"><a href="#PIP安装" class="headerlink" title="PIP安装"></a>PIP安装</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip 是 Python 的软件包安装程序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py</span><br><span class="line">py2: python get-pip.py --user</span><br><span class="line">py3: python3 get-pip.py --user</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/04/13/5cb1a35ace86d.png" alt="a7.png"></p><h2 id="相关python库安装-1"><a href="#相关python库安装-1" class="headerlink" title="相关python库安装"></a>相关python库安装</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">需要安装一下模块</span><br><span class="line">pillow</span><br><span class="line">pyecharts</span><br><span class="line">itchat</span><br><span class="line">jieba</span><br><span class="line">echarts-china-provinces-pypkg</span><br><span class="line">echarts-countries-pypkg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Github项目介绍"><a href="#Github项目介绍" class="headerlink" title="Github项目介绍"></a>Github项目介绍</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://github.com/loadchange/amemv-crawler</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
